-- Monti to Meet Banks, Hedge Funds in London, Corriere Reports
-- B y   C h i a r a   R e m o n d i n i
-- 2012-01-08T11:17:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-08/monti-to-meet-banks-hedge-funds-in-london-corriere-reports.html
Italian Prime Minister  Mario Monti 
plans to meet financial institutions in  London  on Jan. 18 after
a gathering with U.K. Prime Minister David Cameron, daily
newspaper  Corriere della Sera  reported.  Monti will explain the measures taken by his government to
bankers and  hedge funds , Corriere reported, without saying how
it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Remondini in Milan at 
 cremondini@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  